CLM.jl
======

CLM.jl is a Julia port of the Community Land Model (CLM5 / CTSM), the land
surface component of the Community Earth System Model (CESM), originally
developed in Fortran by the National Center for Atmospheric Research (NCAR)
and the broader CESM community.

Original work:
  Community Terrestrial Systems Model (CTSM) / Community Land Model (CLM5)
  https://github.com/ESCOMP/CTSM

Because CLM.jl is a translation (and therefore a derivative work) of the CTSM
Fortran source, the original copyright notice, license conditions, and
disclaimer of the upstream code are reproduced below and are retained in
this distribution as required by that license.

